—ظTarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/job_describe.mdظ@e5f92a8378e9dfa3aa261ca48fc495dc5e803135cc469e679d1f7cd6e4227d83³title: job describe‘¨ExamplesعDescribe a newly spawned job.
